item.title: Unhandled packet 164
item.dc:creator: @XRangdaltonX XRangdaltonX
item.description:
@XRangdaltonX wrote:

Solution : Somewhere in there you deleted case 164. Go to case 98, and put above it “case 164:” without quotations. MAKE SURE CASE 98 IS " Walk on command"

Read full topic
